<h3>Option 2</h3>

<p>Use Homebrew to install tree command, first you need to install Homebrew, you can reference <a href="http://www.mrxuri.com/2014/02/02/install-homebrew-on-os-x.html">Install Homebrew on OS X</a>.</p>

